channel.title: Teamprise V1.1 Released
channel.description: Today we released Teamprise V1.1 to the general public (available here).  Version 1.1 is a maintenance release to address several issues that our customers have reported. Most notably, Version 1.1 now fully supports NTLM authentication (including NTLMv2). If you were...
